      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "import pandas as pd\n",
        "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n",
        "from scipy.stats import chi2_contingency\n",
        "\n",
        "# --- Calcul du tableau de contingence ---\n",
        "contingency = pd.crosstab(df['genotype'], df['severity_class'])\n",
        "\n",
        "# --- Test du χ² ---\n",
        "chi2, p_val, dof, expected = chi2_contingency(contingency)\n",
        "\n",
        "# --- Calcul des proportions par génotype ---\n",
        "proportions = contingency.div(contingency.sum(axis=1), axis=0)\n",
        "\n",
        "# --- Réorganisation des classes et groupes si nécessaire ---\n",
        "class_order = ['léger', 'modéré', 'sévère']\n",
        "group_order = ['WT', 'Het', 'KO']  # Modifier selon tes groupes présents\n",
        "proportions = proportions.reindex(group_order).dropna()\n",
        "colors = ['#a6d96a', '#fdae61', '#d7191c']  # vert, orange, rouge\n",
        "\n",
        "# --- Création du graphique ---\n",
        "fig, ax = plt.subplots(figsize=(8, 6))\n",
        "proportions[class_order].plot(\n",
        "    kind='bar',\n",
        "    stacked=True,\n",
        "    color=colors,\n",
        "    ax=ax,\n",
        "    edgecolor='black'\n",
        ")\n",
        "\n",
        "# --- Annotations des pourcentages ---\n",
        "for i, (genotype, row) in enumerate(proportions.iterrows()):\n",
        "    y_offset = 0\n",
        "    for cls in class_order:\n",
        "        value = row[cls]\n",
        "        if value > 0.05:\n",
        "            ax.text(\n",
        "                x=i,\n",
        "                y=y_offset + value / 2,\n",
        "                s=f\"{value:.0%}\",\n",
        "                ha='center',\n",
        "                va='center',\n",
        "                color='black',\n",
        "                fontsize=11\n",
        "            )\n",
        "        y_offset += value\n",
        "\n",
        "# --- Esthétique ---\n",
        "ax.set_title(f\"Répartition des classes de sévérité par génotype\\nTest du χ² : p = {p_val:.4f}\", fontsize=16)\n",
        "ax.set_ylabel(\"Proportion\", fontsize=14)\n",
        "ax.set_xlabel(\"Génotype\", fontsize=14)\n",
        "ax.set_xticklabels([tick.get_text() for tick in ax.get_xticklabels()], rotation=0, fontsize=12)\n",
        "ax.set_yticks([0.0, 0.25, 0.5, 0.75, 1.0])\n",
        "ax.set_yticklabels([f\"{int(y*100)}%\" for y in ax.get_yticks()], fontsize=12)\n",
        "ax.legend(title=\"Classe de sévérité\", fontsize=11, title_fontsize=12, loc=\"upper right\")\n",
        "\n",
        "plt.tight_layout()\n",
        "plt.savefig(\"barres_empilees_statistiques.png\", dpi=600)\n",
        "plt.show()"
